description: Analytics grouped by data source, event group, and annotations. Monitor ingress, egress, errors, filtered and cancelled files.

targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
  time_bucket_gapfill(($__interval_ms || ' ms')::interval, time, start => $__timeFrom(), finish => $__timeTo()) AS time,
  CASE 
    WHEN '${annotationKey}' = 'All' THEN datasource_name || ' - ' || group_name
    ELSE datasource_name || ' - ' || group_name || ' - ' || annotation_value
  END AS series_name,
  COALESCE(SUM(ingress_bytes), 0) AS ingress_bytes,
  COALESCE(SUM(ingress_files), 0) AS ingress_files,
  COALESCE(SUM(egress_bytes), 0) AS egress_bytes,
  COALESCE(SUM(egress_files), 0) AS egress_files,
  COALESCE(SUM(error_files), 0) AS error_files,
  COALESCE(SUM(filter_files), 0) AS filter_files
FROM get_analytics_data(
  '${annotationKey}',
  ARRAY[$annotationValues],
  ARRAY[$dataSources],
  ARRAY[$groups],
  ARRAY[$analyticIngressTypes],
  $__timeFrom(),
  $__timeTo(),
  ($__interval_ms || ' ms')
)
GROUP BY 1, 2
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  datasource_name AS "Data Source",
  group_name AS "Group",
  CASE 
    WHEN '${annotationKey}' != 'All' THEN annotation_value 
  END AS "Annotation Value",
  SUM(ingress_bytes) AS "Ingress Bytes",
  SUM(ingress_files) AS "Ingress Files",
  SUM(egress_bytes) AS "Egress Bytes",
  SUM(egress_files) AS "Egress Files",
  SUM(error_files) AS "Errored",
  SUM(filter_files) AS "Filtered"
FROM get_analytics_data(
  '${annotationKey}',
  ARRAY[$annotationValues],
  ARRAY[$dataSources],
  ARRAY[$groups],
  ARRAY[$analyticIngressTypes],
  $__timeFrom(),
  $__timeTo(),
  '100 years'
)
GROUP BY 
  datasource_name, 
  group_name,
  CASE 
    WHEN '${annotationKey}' != 'All' THEN annotation_value 
  END
ORDER BY "Data Source", "Group", "Annotation Value";

list.definition:
SELECT DISTINCT 
  fd.name AS __value,
  fd.name AS __text
FROM (
    SELECT DISTINCT aa.data_source_id
    FROM analytics_5m_anno aa 
    WHERE $__timeFilter(aa.bucket_start)
    UNION
    SELECT DISTINCT an.data_source_id
    FROM analytics_5m_noanno an
    WHERE $__timeFilter(an.bucket_start)
) a
JOIN flow_definitions fd
ON fd.id = a.data_source_id;
list.label: Data Sources
list.name: dataSources
list.query:
SELECT DISTINCT 
  fd.name AS __value,
  fd.name AS __text
FROM (
    SELECT DISTINCT aa.data_source_id
    FROM analytics_5m_anno aa 
    WHERE $__timeFilter(aa.bucket_start)
    UNION
    SELECT DISTINCT an.data_source_id
    FROM analytics_5m_noanno an
    WHERE $__timeFilter(an.bucket_start)
) a
JOIN flow_definitions fd
ON fd.id = a.data_source_id;

list.definition:
SELECT DISTINCT
  eg.name AS __text,
  eg.name AS __value
FROM (
  SELECT event_group_id, data_source_id, bucket_start
  FROM analytics_5m_anno
  UNION ALL
  SELECT event_group_id, data_source_id, bucket_start
  FROM analytics_5m_noanno
) a
JOIN flow_definitions fd ON a.data_source_id = fd.id
JOIN event_groups eg ON a.event_group_id = eg.id
WHERE $__timeFilter(a.bucket_start)
  AND ('All' in ($dataSources) OR fd.name in ($dataSources));

list.definition:
SELECT DISTINCT
  ak.key_name AS __text,
  ak.key_name AS __value
FROM analytics_5m_anno aa
JOIN flow_definitions fd ON aa.data_source_id = fd.id
JOIN event_groups eg ON aa.event_group_id = eg.id
JOIN annotation_keys ak ON aa.annotation_key_id = ak.id
WHERE $__timeFilter(aa.bucket_start)
  AND ('All' IN ($dataSources) OR fd.name IN ($dataSources))
  AND ('All' IN ($groups) OR eg.name IN ($groups))

list.definition:
SELECT DISTINCT
  av.value_text AS __text,
  av.value_text AS __value
FROM analytics_5m_anno aa
JOIN flow_definitions fd ON aa.data_source_id = fd.id
JOIN event_groups eg ON aa.event_group_id = eg.id
JOIN annotation_keys ak ON aa.annotation_key_id = ak.id
JOIN annotation_values av ON aa.annotation_value_id = av.id
WHERE $__timeFilter(aa.bucket_start)
  AND ('All' IN ($dataSources) OR fd.name IN ($dataSources))
  AND ('All' IN ($groups) OR eg.name IN ($groups))
  AND ak.key_name = '${annotationKey}' 
  AND '${annotationKey}' != 'All'
